name: Midnight Owl tote bag
description:
Our designs have been hand drawn and digitally developed and then printed onto unbleached cotton tote bags. Our Midnight owl design includes a repeated owl pattern.

Our Tote bags are perfect size for students carrying their university equipment, as well as being perfect for use as a shopping bag.

A strong, durable and eco friendly alternative to plastic shopping bags which can be used again and again without harming the environment - made from 100% biodegradable cotton. 100% 110 gsm cotton. 

Dimensions: 42cm x 38cm

- Our bags are machine washable, for best washing results, hand wash or machine wash at around 30 degrees. Turn the bag inside out to protect the image and do not tumble dry, instead hang dry.

- If ironing is required, place non thick baking paper over the image and remember to remove this straight after ironing.
